Te reo ʻia e paraparauhia nei i niʻa i te motu nō [[Tahiti]].
Nō te mea hoʻi ʻua riro teie motu ʻei pū mātāmua nō te mau taʻa motu o [[Pōrīnetia farāni]], e pūʻohu-noa-hia ia te mau reo toʻopae a te mau taʻa motu i roto i teie pātete "[[reo Māʻohi]]".

Te tanoraʻa mau e au ʻia faʻataʻahia te reo Tahiti, te [[reo ʻEnana]], te [[reo Paʻumotu]], te [[reo Maʻareva]] ʻe te [[reo Tuhaʻa pae]].

